  Added a patch to fix some annoying bugs, and bumped into stable for x86,
  sparc, and mips.

*crossdev-0.4 (30 Jan 2004)

  30 Jan 2004; Joshua Kinard <kumba@gentoo.org> crossdev-0.4.ebuild:
